OOC: yes, i agree that all Transformers are equal under Primus' eye.  
Remember, he created both Autobots and Decepticons, to fight his enemy 
Unicron, and, I pretty much think of the pit as a Cybertronian swear, equal 
to hell.  When people say, "What the hell?" they usually don't have the fiery 
underworld in mind.
